p.k: After Starfire is set up by Blackfire and sent to prison, the Titans work to make Blackfire a better sister while Starfire plots her revenge. / When Robin gets frustrated with the Titans' disobedience he turns to...puppets. / Robin dabbles with magic, ignoring Raven's warning that he will anger the magic god. / Using a grandma voice, Cyborg makes the others dress warmly. / A giant cocoon mysteriously appears in the Titans' living room and no one can find Beast Boy.
